ont-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                من نوقش الحساب عذب قالت قلت يقول الله تعالى فسوف يحاسب حسابا يسيرا قال ذلك العرض\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, he who is subjected to a detailed reckoning [hisab] will be punished. They said, \"I said, 'Allah, the Most High, says: \"He will be brought to an easy reckoning [hisaban yasira].\"'\" He said, \"That is the presentation [al-'ard].\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"وَيَنْقَلِبُ","d":"ُbِlَqnَyَw","e":"ُbِlَqnَyَw"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.02","c":"إِلَى","d":"ٰٓàَlِiʾ","e":"ٰٓàَlِiʾ"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.14","c":"أَهْلِهِ","d":"ۦِhِlْhَaʾ","e":"ۦِhِlْhَaʾ"},{"b":"4.8","h":"6.95","c":"مَسْرُورًا","d":"āًrwُrْsَm","e":"āًrwُrْsَm"}],"a":{"g":"And return to his people in happiness."}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.43","c":"وَأَمَّا","d":"āَّmَaʾَw","e":"āَّmَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.38","c":"مَنْ","d":"ْnَm","e":"ْnَm"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.16","c":"أُوتِيَ","d":"َàِtwُaʾ","e":"َàِtwُaʾ"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.43","c":"كِتَابَهُ","d":"ۥُhَbَٰtِk","e":"ۥُhَbَٰtِk"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.86","c":"وَرَاءَ","d":"َءٓāَrَw","e":"َءٓāَrَw"},{"b":"6.7","h":"9.12","c":"ظَهْرِهِ","d":"ۦِhِrْhَẓ","e":"ۦِhِrْhَẓ"}],"a":{"g":"But as for he who is given his record behind his back,"}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"فَسَوْفَ","d":"َfْwَsَf","e":"َfْwَsَf"},{"b":"0.72","h":"1.63","c":"يَدْعُوا","d":"۟āwُʿعْdَy","e":"۟āwُʿعْdَy"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.06","c":"ثُبُورًا","d":"āًrwُbُht","e":"āًrwُbُht"}],"a":{"g":"He will cry out for destruction"}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.45","c":"وَيَصْلَى","d":"ٰàَlْṣَyَw","e":"ٰàَlْṣَyَw"},{"b":"0.94","h":"2.21","c":"سَعِيرًا","d":"āًryِʿعَs","e":"āًryِʿ